'''''Road to Revival''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[Herta Space Station]].

==Steps==
# Head to the base zone and help the researcher in need
# Activate the extinguished anchor in the target cabin
# Let Abraham know that the anchor is operational again
# Make your way through the locked cabin infested with Legion abominations
# Go to the storage zone and learn about the revival declared by researchers
# Repair the gap and take out the Legion abomination at the end of the path
# Return to the safe zone and report the results to Hinkel

